libhnj
------------------------------------------
Libhnj is a library for high quality hyphenation and justification.

Runtime requirements:
  bash-4.3.39-2
  cygwin-2.0.4-1
  libhnj-devel-0.1.1-1bl1
  libhnj0-0.1.1-1bl1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-13-1
  automake-9-1
  binutils-2.25-2
  cygport-0.20.1-1
  gcc-core-4.9.2-3
  libtool-2.4.6-1
  make-4.1-1

Canonical website:
  http://hkn.eecs.berkeley.edu/~dyoo/pyHnj/

Canonical download:
  http://hkn.eecs.berkeley.edu/~dyoo/pyHnj/libhnj-0.1.1.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack libhnj-0.1.1-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./libhnj-0.1.1-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/libhnj-0.1.1-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libhnj-0.1.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libhnj0-0.1.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libhnj-devel-0.1.1-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(libhnj)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/libhnj.README
  /usr/share/doc/libhnj/AUTHORS
  /usr/share/doc/libhnj/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/libhnj/ChangeLog
  /usr/share/doc/libhnj/NEWS
  /usr/share/doc/libhnj/README

(libhnj0)
  /usr/bin/cyghnj-0.dll

(libhnj-devel)
  /usr/bin/libhnj-config
  /usr/include/libhnj/hqjust.h
  /usr/include/libhnj/hsjust.h
  /usr/include/libhnj/hyphen.h
  /usr/include/libhnj/just.h
  /usr/lib/libhnj.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/libhnj.pc
  /usr/share/aclocal/libhnj.m4

